âœ… 3. Frontend (React) Naming Conventions
Folders

Use lowercase with hyphens:

src/
  components/
  pages/
  hooks/
  utils/
  assets/
  styles/

React Components

âœ” PascalCase for component files and folders

UserCard.jsx
LoginForm.jsx
DashboardPage.jsx


âœ” Files inside a component folder:

UserCard/
  index.jsx
  user-card.jsx
  user-card.css

Other files

âœ” camelCase for utilities & hooks:

fetchUser.js
useAuth.js
formatDate.js

âœ… 4. Backend (Java / Spring Boot)
Java Package Structure

âœ” Always use lowercase + dot notation
âœ” No underscores, no hyphens

com.l0gn3.lifemanlog
com.l0gn3.stealthagon
com.l0gn3.artelligenie

Folder Structure
src/main/java/com/l0gn3/app/
    controller/
    service/
    repository/
    config/
    model/
src/main/resources/
    application.yml

Class naming

âœ” PascalCase

UserController.java
